metadata.name: F Flower
metadata.description: This flower symbolizes remembrance, true love, and loyalty. The flower is associated with the idea of unforgettable memories and enduring affection, as well as with the notion of steadfastness and loyalty in relationships. At the same time, this flower can also be seen as a symbol of hope, as its tiny but vibrant blooms remind us that even the smallest act of kindness or love can have a lasting impact. With their timeless beauty and sentimental significance, this flower is a cherished symbol that holds a special place in the hearts of many.
